        public void onActionAppointmentCancel​(javafx.event.ActionEvent event)
                               throws java.io.IOException
        An Action Handler that change scene to Main Form. Using a constant enum, FxmlPath.MAIN_FORM the point of change is limited when updated, thus, limiting bugs when changes to fxml path file occurs.
        Parameters:
        event - action event
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException - if file is not found, throws an IOException. Since it is part of the code base, User will not notice this error unless they intentionally rename the file or delete it. If error does occur, an error dialog will pop up
